{
  "id": "RAW_a75e9ef7",
  "title": "为什么一切终将分崩离析",
  "url": "https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/why-things-will-eventually-fall-apart",
  "date": "2026-06-02 23:41:57",
  "author": "Gary Marcus",
  "siteName": "Marcus on AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Part I: The Math\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p>1. Everybody, even Google, seems to be treating AI as if it were some kind of winner take all competition like web search was, in which Google taking over 90%</p>\n   <p>2. But everybody is building essentially the same technical solution with essentially the same data, so there is no moat.</p>\n   <p>3. If there is no moat, nobody is going to take 90% of the market.</p>\n   <p>4. With no clear winners, nobody can charge monopoly prices; instead, you get price wars and commodity pricing.</p>\n   <p>5. Which means everybody will wind up overpaying compared to the modest profits they will be able to make in an intensely competitive regime.</p>\n   <p>Am I missing something?</p>\n   <p></p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Part II: The Psychology\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p>None of that would matter in the near term if people weren’t noticing.</p>\n   <p>But they are. Consider:</p>\n   <ol>\n    <li>\n     <p><span>When </span><a href=\"https://x.com/garymarcus/status/2061617157897912370?s=61\">I posted the above last night on X</a><span>, sparked </span><a href=\"https://x.com/dee_bosa/status/2061576639713346042?s=61\">by the jawdropping announcement that Google of all places was raising equity financing</a><span> , over 750,000 (and counting) viewed the tweet overnight. And what’s more most people agreed, which in that crowd is very rare.</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span>The financial world is taking a lot more notice of my skepticism than it used to. Just yesterday two significant (and excellent) podcasts with me just dropped, </span><a href=\"https://youtu.be/NRSvQqG6BgE?si=Ovfm2dUMNloHfWiL\">a return to the show hosted by the well-known Steve Eisman</a><span> (played by Steve Carrell in The Big Short): and the other a four-hander with the well-known investor </span><a href=\"https://open.substack.com/pub/georgenoble/p/ai-the-biggest-capital-misallocation-d18?r=8tdk6&amp;utm_campaign=post-expanded-share&amp;utm_medium=web\">George Noble, the economist Julie Garran and the financial analyst/reporter who is known in the youtube world as @nobodyspecial</a><span>. Everyone involved in both podcasts share my concerns, and had sharp arguments of their own to add. Garran’s distillation of why the LLM industry will never be commercially viable was crystal clear and compelling. </span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>My critique of tokenmaxxing is getting picked up, too; everybody seems to think that trend is over. And companies like Anthropic are ending their all you can eat buffet, which will make many customers think twice.</p>\n     <a href=\"https://x.com/garymarcus/status/2061636801794892147?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n        <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n         <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n          <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 1x, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e896d385-456a-44b9-583e-edf1d3c7a300/public 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg\" alt=\"X avatar for @GaryMarcus\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 1x, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3be24ccf-5e2d-4967-a697-2e8865999b00/public 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 3x\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Gary Marcus</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@GaryMarcus</span>\n        </div>\n        <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n         <g>\n          <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n         </g>\n        </svg>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">“Tokens got burned for millions of dollars without any real significant ROI to show for it,” one tech executive put it in a social post Marcus cited. The phrase reads less like a complaint than an epitaph.”</div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset bg-black-dCpgGg outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-sm overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 container-aGHQ9p\">\n        <img src=\"https://pbs.substack.com/media/HJxnvvBbIAA7eUj.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"image-c_FmAR\">\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">2:31 AM · Jun 2, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">8.45K Views</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">9 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">38 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">170 Likes</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>Still more reports have coming out questioning the RoI for corporate customers. Bain’s conclusions yesterday almost perfectly the old definition of insanity that I keep quoting (doing the same thing over and over again and expecting different results):</p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_68d9e2b7-29a5-4607-a858-552cc9d72942_1369x582.jpeg\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_68d9e2b7-29a5-4607-a858-552cc9d72942_1369x582.jpeg 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fc0157e0-7b15-4544-236d-68e1ced48200/public 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_68d9e2b7-29a5-4607-a858-552cc9d72942_1369x582.jpeg 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_68d9e2b7-29a5-4607-a858-552cc9d72942_1369x582.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/963fc09b-07c4-4dc7-38d3-46274302c200/public\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_68d9e2b7-29a5-4607-a858-552cc9d72942_1369x582.jpeg 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6584aa1b-15bc-4ff3-e645-c92733023300/public 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_68d9e2b7-29a5-4607-a858-552cc9d72942_1369x582.jpeg 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/963fc09b-07c4-4dc7-38d3-46274302c200/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_00b6cdf0-b795-4b7b-a6e0-c8c14fe087ab_1488x1009.png\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_00b6cdf0-b795-4b7b-a6e0-c8c14fe087ab_1488x1009.png 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b3fd98fc-fa4e-4398-a79f-59c47a6dba00/public 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_00b6cdf0-b795-4b7b-a6e0-c8c14fe087ab_1488x1009.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_00b6cdf0-b795-4b7b-a6e0-c8c14fe087ab_1488x1009.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/61644878-6723-42b5-18c9-d1d8eb37de00/public\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_00b6cdf0-b795-4b7b-a6e0-c8c14fe087ab_1488x1009.png 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/86f065e3-d73e-4241-cf8e-2e6e509ae100/public 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_00b6cdf0-b795-4b7b-a6e0-c8c14fe087ab_1488x1009.png 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/61644878-6723-42b5-18c9-d1d8eb37de00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n   <p>§</p>\n   <p>Timing when all this might fall apart is hard, but the economics don’t make sense, and more and more people are starting to notice.</p>\n   <p>What is most upsetting though, is how retail investors and retirement funds are likely to be taken advantage of in all of this.</p>\n   <a href=\"https://x.com/egrefen/status/2061179992784982137?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n      <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n       <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n        <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_8_FxlWxz.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_8_FxlWxz.jpg 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_8_FxlWxz.jpg 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_8_FxlWxz.jpg\" alt=\"X avatar for @egrefen\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_8_FxlWxz.jpg 1x, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a73de926-8a0e-4a2d-dd42-c75452f9a700/public 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_8_FxlWxz.jpg 3x\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Edward Grefenstette</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@egrefen</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n       <g>\n        <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n       </g>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">SpaceX being rammed into indices with no profit requirements, seasoning, and generally looser constraints is economic terrorism. Index trackers will eat the loss when reality catches up and retail investors will suffer.</div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">8:16 PM · May 31, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">181K Views</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">59 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">649 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">5.02K Likes</span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p>Same will happen with Anthropic and OpenAI. All of which led me to this prediction yesterday:</p>\n   <a href=\"https://x.com/garymarcus/status/2061505704503206107?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n      <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n       <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n        <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 1x, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e896d385-456a-44b9-583e-edf1d3c7a300/public 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg\" alt=\"X avatar for @GaryMarcus\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 1x, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3be24ccf-5e2d-4967-a697-2e8865999b00/public 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 3x\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Gary Marcus</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@GaryMarcus</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n       <g>\n        <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n       </g>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">Prediction: Nobody knows when this will all collapse, but 2026 will be remembered in hindsight as the year in which retail investors and index funds were left holding the bag.</div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset elevatedTheme-fBklGV\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-padding-12 pc-boxShadow-none pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-sm sizing-border-box-DggLA4\">\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-8 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n        <div style=\"--scale:20px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-20 pc-height-20 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n         <div style=\"--scale:20px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-20 pc-height-20 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n          <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_zuVxC3sR.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_zuVxC3sR.jpg 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_zuVxC3sR.jpg 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_zuVxC3sR.jpg\" alt=\"X avatar for @hkarthik\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_zuVxC3sR.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_zuVxC3sR.jpg 2x, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/beb8f58c-fbcb-4869-5b48-22b9d3c20600/public 3x\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Karthik Hariharan</span> <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@hkarthik</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">It's funny how people thought raising a mere $50B was going to slow Anthropic from doing an IPO this year. The frontier labs need capital to keep scaling. And they've exhausted the private market's appetite for more risk. They have no choice but to go public.</div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">5:50 PM · Jun 1, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">108K Views</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">43 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">153 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">1.3K Likes</span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p>I seriously hope that I am wrong about this. But I doubt it.</p>\n   <div id=\"youtube2-NRSvQqG6BgE\" class=\"youtube-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"youtube-inner\">\n     <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/NRSvQqG6BgE?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>To close, here’s one more economist, </span><span style=\"min-width:0;\"><a href=\"https://open.substack.com/users/16879-brad-delong?utm_source=mentions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"mention-pnpTE1\">Brad DeLong</a></span><span> </span><a href=\"https://open.substack.com/pub/braddelong/p/inference-is-unlikely-to-ever-be?r=8tdk6&amp;utm_medium=ios\">reaching basically the same conclusions</a><span>; I leave the last words with him:</span></p>\n   <p><em>The technology is powerful but unreliable. It must be boxed into narrow, supervised uses. The economics of inference are unforgiving. The competitive environment is crowded, with open models and vertically integrated hyperscalers eroding any pricing power that an independent lab might hope to have.</em></p>\n   <p><em>What is the plausible, well‑specified path by which Anthropic or OpenAI grow into the kind of durable, high‑margin franchises that would justify the valuations their private rounds have implied?</em></p>\n   <p><em>There is none visible.</em></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <div class=\"subscribe-widget\">\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-justifyContent-center pc-reset\">\n     <div class=\"container-IpPqBD\">\n      <form action=\"/api/v1/free?nojs=true\" method=\"post\" novalidate class=\"form form-M5sC90\">\n       <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_url\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_referrer\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_url\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_referrer\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_url\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_referrer\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referral_code\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"subscribe-widget\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referring_pub_id\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"additional_referring_pub_ids\">\n       <div class=\"sideBySideWrap-vGXrwP\">\n        <div class=\"emailInputWrapper-QlA86j\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-minWidth-0 pc-position-relative pc-reset flex-auto-j3S2WA\">\n          <input name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Type your email...\" type=\"email\" class=\"pencraft emailInput-OkIMeB input-y4v6N4 inputText-pV_yWb\">\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"submit\" disabled class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft rightButton primary subscribe-btn button-VFSdkv buttonBase-GK1x3M\"><span class=\"button-text\">Subscribe</span></button>\n       </div>\n      </form>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"embedded-post-wrap\">\n    <a href=\"https://georgenoble.substack.com/p/ai-the-biggest-capital-misallocation-d18?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_campaign=post_embed&amp;utm_medium=web\" class=\"embedded-post\"> \n     <div class=\"embedded-post-header\">\n      <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260602164310_c0c7b1b3-6034-4f5f-8ef5-eeaf9bbfbe2a_55x55.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"embedded-post-publication-logo\"><span class=\"embedded-post-publication-name\">The Noble Update</span>\n     </div> \n     <div class=\"embedded-post-title-wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"embedded-post-title\">AI: The Biggest Capital Misallocation in History</div>\n     </div> \n     <div class=\"embedded-post-cta-wrapper\">\n      <span class=\"embedded-post-cta\">Read more</span>\n     </div> \n     <div class=\"embedded-post-meta\">18 hours ago · 31 likes · 1 comment · George Noble</div> \n    </a>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Gary Marcus 认为，AI 行业正走向崩溃，因为所有人都在用同样的数据构建同样的东西，没有护城河，导致商品化定价，最终让散户投资者接盘。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Gary Marcus 认为，AI 行业正走向崩溃，因为所有人都在用同样的数据构建同样的东西，没有护城河，导致商品化定价，最终让散户投资者接盘。",
  "summary": "本文提出了一个两部分论证，解释为什么当前的 AI 热潮不可持续。第一部分阐述了数学逻辑：由于所有主要参与者（Google、OpenAI、Anthropic）都在用相同的数据构建本质上相同的技术，因此不存在竞争护城河。没有护城河，就没有哪家公司能主导市场或收取垄断价格，从而导致价格战和商品化。这意味着巨额资本支出将永远无法收回。第二部分认为，金融界开始注意到这一现实，并引用了病毒式传播的社交媒体互动、与知名投资者的播客节目以及 Bain 等咨询公司质疑 ROI 的报告。Marcus 强调了散户投资者和指数基金面临的风险，当泡沫破裂时，他们可能会成为接盘侠，并以经济学家 Brad DeLong 的引述作为结尾：他认为前沿实验室没有一条合理的路径来证明其估值的合理性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 行业缺乏竞争护城河。",
      "explanation": "所有主要参与者都在用相同的数据构建相同的技术解决方案，这使得任何一家公司都无法获得主导市场份额或收取垄断价格。"
    },
    {
      "point": "商品化将导致价格战和低利润。",
      "explanation": "在没有明确赢家的情况下，市场将变成一个竞争激烈的商品业务，使得公司无法收回其巨额资本投资。"
    },
    {
      "point": "金融市场开始认识到其不可持续性。",
      "explanation": "病毒式传播的社交媒体帖子、与知名投资者的播客节目以及 Bain 等公司的报告越来越多地质疑 AI 的 ROI，表明市场情绪正在转变。"
    },
    {
      "point": "散户投资者和指数基金面临最大风险。",
      "explanation": "随着私募市场枯竭，前沿实验室被迫上市，指数基金被迫持有其股票，当市场回调来临时，普通投资者将承担损失。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "如果没有护城河，没有人能占据 90% 的市场份额。",
    "这项技术强大但不可靠。它必须被限制在狭窄、受监督的用途中。推理的经济学是残酷的。",
    "Anthropic 或 OpenAI 有什么合理且明确的路径，能够成长为那种持久的、高利润的特许经营企业，从而证明其私募轮次所暗示的估值是合理的？没有一条是可见的。"
  ],
